data class FreeClassBook(
    val title: String,
    val author: String,
    val category: String,
    val coverUrl: String,
    val description: String,
    val sourceUrl: String,
    val textEnglish: String
)

val curatedFreeBooks = listOf(
    FreeClassBook(
        title = "The Adventures of Sherlock Holmes",
        author = "Sir Arthur Conan Doyle",
        category = "Mystery",
        coverUrl = "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1513002749550-c59d786b8e6c?w=500",
        description = "A collection of twelve classic detective stories featuring Arthur Conan Doyle's famous consulting detective Sherlock Holmes.",
        sourceUrl = "https://www.gutenberg.org/ebooks/1661",
        textEnglish = """
            Chapter 1 - A Scandal in Bohemia
            
            To Sherlock Holmes she is always the woman. I have seldom heard him mention her under any other name. In his eyes she eclipses and predominates the whole of her sex. It was not that he felt any emotion akin to love for Irene Adler. All emotions, and that one particularly, were abhorrent to his cold, precise but admirably balanced mind. He was, I take it, the most perfect reasoning and observing machine that the world has seen, but as a lover he would have placed himself in a false position. He never spoke of the softer passions, save with a gibe and a sneer. They were admirable things for the observer—excellent for drawing the veil from men’s motives and actions. But for the trained reasoner to admit such intrusions into his own delicate and finely adjusted temperament was to introduce a distracting factor which might throw a doubt upon all his mental results. Grit in a sensitive instrument, or a crack in one of his own high-power lenses, would not be more disturbing than a strong emotion in a nature such as his. And yet there was but one woman to him, and that woman was the late Irene Adler, of dubious and questionable memory.
            
            Chapter 2 - Case of Identity
            
            "My dear fellow," said Sherlock Holmes as we sat on either side of the hearth in his lodgings in Baker Street, "life is infinitely stranger than anything which the mind of man could invent. We would not dare to conceive the things which are really mere commonplaces of existence. If we could fly out of that window hand in hand, hover over this great city, gently remove the roofs, and peep in at the peculiarities, the coincidences, the plannings, the cross-purposes, the wonderful chains of events, working through generations, and leading to the most outre results, it would make all fiction with its conventionalities and foreseen conclusions most stale and unprofitable."
        """.trimIndent()
    ),
    FreeClassBook(
        title = "Alice's Adventures in Wonderland",
        author = "Lewis Carroll",
        category = "Fantasy",
        coverUrl = "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1544947950-fa07a98d237f?w=500",
        description = "A standard Victorian fantasy of a curious girl named Alice who falls through a rabbit hole into a fantastical world.",
        sourceUrl = "https://www.gutenberg.org/ebooks/11",
        textEnglish = """
            Chapter 1 - Down the Rabbit-Hole
            
            Alice was beginning to get very tired of sitting by her sister on the bank, and of having nothing to do: once or twice she had peeped into the book her sister was reading, but it had no pictures or conversations in it, “and what is the use of a book,” thought Alice “without pictures or conversations?”
            
            So she was considering in her own mind (as well as she could, for the hot day made her feel very sleepy and stupid), whether the pleasure of making a daisy-chain would be worth the trouble of getting up and picking the daisies, when suddenly a White Rabbit with pink eyes ran close by her.
            
            There was nothing so VERY remarkable in that; nor did Alice think it so VERY much out of the way to hear the Rabbit say to itself, “Oh dear! Oh dear! I shall be late!” (when she thought it over afterwards, it occurred to her that she ought to have wondered at this, but at the time it all seemed quite natural); but when the Rabbit actually TOOK A WATCH OUT OF ITS WAISTCOAT-POCKET, and looked at it, and then hurried on, Alice started to her feet, for it flashed across her mind that she had never before seen a rabbit with either a waistcoat-pocket, or a watch to take out of it, and burning with curiosity, she ran across the field after it, and fortunately was just in time to see it pop down a large rabbit-hole under the hedge.
        """.trimIndent()
    ),
    FreeClassBook(
        title = "The Time Machine",
        author = "H. G. Wells",
        category = "Sci-Fi",
        coverUrl = "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1451187580459-43490279c0fa?w=500",
        description = "A pioneering science-fiction novel where a Victorian scientist travels hundreds of thousands of years into future earth.",
        sourceUrl = "https://www.gutenberg.org/ebooks/35",
        textEnglish = """
            Chapter 1 - Introduction
            
            The Time Traveller (for so it will be convenient to speak of him) was expounding a recondite matter to us. His grey eyes shone and twinkled, and his usually pale face was flushed and animated. The fire burned brightly, and the soft radiance of the incandescent lights in the lilies of silver caught the bubbles that flashed and passed in our glasses. Our chairs, being his patrons, were habitually luxurious and comfortable, and we were disposed to be quite cozy.
            
            And he put it to us in this way—marking the points with a lean forefinger—as we sat and watched him: "You must follow me carefully. I shall have to controvert one or two ideas that are almost universally accepted. The geometry, for instance, they taught you at school is founded on a misconception."
        """.trimIndent()
    ),
    FreeClassBook(
        title = "Bhagavad Gita",
        author = "Vyasa",
        category = "Spiritual",
        coverUrl = "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1609137144813-9ecf79fc7347?w=500",
        description = "Universal, timeless philosophical and spiritual teachings of Lord Krishna to warrior Arjuna on the battlefield of Kurukshetra.",
        sourceUrl = "https://www.gutenberg.org/ebooks/2388",
        textEnglish = """
            Chapter 1 - The Grief of Arjuna
            
            Dhritarashtra said: On the holy plain of Kurukshetra, gathered together and eager for battle, what did my people and the Pandavas do, O Sanjaya?
            
            Sanjaya said: Having seen the army of the Pandavas drawn up in battle array, King Duryodhana then approached his teacher Drona and spoke these words. Duryodhana pointed out the grand heroes and master archers present.
            
            Arjuna, seeing his own kinsmen, teachers, grandfathers, and friends assembled on both sides ready to fight each other, felt deep compassion and said: "My limbs fail, my mouth is parched, my body trembles and my hair stands on end. I see no good in killing my own kinsmen in battle."
        """.trimIndent()
    )
)

@Composable
fun EBookLibraryWidget(viewModel: MainViewModel) {
    val context = LocalContext.current
    val coroutineScope = rememberCoroutineScope()
    var searchQuery by remember { mutableStateOf("") }
    
    var selectedBookForReading by remember { mutableStateOf<FreeClassBook?>(null) }
    var isAILoadingBySearch by remember { mutableStateOf(false) }

    Surface(
        shape = RoundedCornerShape(24.dp),
        color = Color(0xFF070B18),
        modifier = Modifier
            .fillMaxWidth()
            .border(1.5.dp, CyberCyan.copy(alpha = 0.8f), RoundedCornerShape(24.dp))
            .padding(2.dp)
            .testTag("ebook_library_section")
    ) {
        Column(modifier = Modifier.padding(14.dp), verticalArrangement = Arrangement.spacedBy(10.dp)) {
            // Header Row
            Row(
                modifier = Modifier.fillMaxWidth(),
                horizontalArrangement = Arrangement.SpaceBetween,
                verticalAlignment = Alignment.CenterVertically
            ) {
                Row(verticalAlignment = Alignment.CenterVertically, horizontalArrangement = Arrangement.spacedBy(6.dp)) {
                    Text("📚", fontSize = 16.sp)
                    Text("UNLIMITED AI & FREE E-BOOK LIBRARY", fontWeight = FontWeight.Bold, color = Color.White, fontSize = 11.sp, letterSpacing = 0.5.sp)
                }
                Box(
                    modifier = Modifier
                        .background(CyberCyan.copy(alpha = 0.15f), RoundedCornerShape(8.dp))
                        .padding(horizontal = 8.dp, vertical = 2.dp)
                ) {
                    Text("FREE", color = CyberCyan, fontSize = 9.sp, fontWeight = FontWeight.ExtraBold)
                }
            }

            Text("Browse classical masterpieces or search ANY book in the world – our AI details and prepares dynamic offline summaries instantly!", color = TextLight, fontSize = 10.sp)

            // Search Box and Button
            Row(
                modifier = Modifier.fillMaxWidth(),
                verticalAlignment = Alignment.CenterVertically,
                horizontalArrangement = Arrangement.spacedBy(6.dp)
            ) {
                OutlinedTextField(
                    value = searchQuery,
                    onValueChange = { searchQuery = it },
                    modifier = Modifier.weight(1f),
                    colors = OutlinedTextFieldDefaults.colors(
                        focusedTextColor = Color.White,
                        unfocusedTextColor = Color.White,
                        focusedBorderColor = CyberCyan,
                        unfocusedBorderColor = GridSpace
                    ),
                    placeholder = { Text("Search title, author or topics...", color = TextMuted, fontSize = 11.sp) },
                    singleLine = true
                )

                Button(
                    onClick = {
                        if (searchQuery.isNotBlank()) {
                            isAILoadingBySearch = true
                            coroutineScope.launch {
                                try {
                                    val matchedIndex = curatedFreeBooks.indexOfFirst {
                                        it.title.contains(searchQuery, ignoreCase = true) || it.author.contains(searchQuery, ignoreCase = true)
                                    }
                                    if (matchedIndex != -1) {
                                        selectedBookForReading = curatedFreeBooks[matchedIndex]
                                    } else {
                                        val prompt = "Act as a professional e-book library archivist. Write a complete, comprehensive, and highly engaging chapter/summary layout with rich content of 3 detailed chapters/sections in beautiful Hindi/Urdu and English side-by-side for the book: '$searchQuery'. Format with elegant section headers like 'BOOK PREVIEW', 'CHAPTER 1', etc., and double linebreaks. Make it a substantial 500-word beautiful reading experience."
                                        val generatedFullText = viewModel.getLLMResponseForModel(viewModel.selectedModel.value, prompt)
                                        selectedBookForReading = FreeClassBook(
                                            title = searchQuery.replaceFirstChar { it.uppercase() },
                                            author = "AI Virtual Synthesis",
                                            category = "Dynamic Library",
                                            coverUrl = "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1513002749550-c59d786b8e6c?w=500",
                                            description = "Dynamic AI curated mastercopy for reading '$searchQuery' completely for free.",
                                            sourceUrl = "https://www.gutenberg.org",
                                            textEnglish = generatedFullText
                                        )
                                    }
                                } catch (e: Exception) {
                                    Log.e("EBookLibraryWidget", "AI e-book search layout generation failed: ${e.message}")
                                } finally {
                                    isAILoadingBySearch = false
                                }
                            }
                        }
                    },
                    colors = ButtonDefaults.buttonColors(containerColor = CyberCyan),
                    shape = RoundedCornerShape(10.dp),
                    contentPadding = PaddingValues(horizontal = 12.dp)
                ) {
                    if (isAILoadingBySearch) {
                        CircularProgressIndicator(color = Color.Black, modifier = Modifier.size(14.dp), strokeWidth = 2.dp)
                    } else {
                        Text("AI READ", color = Color.Black, fontWeight = FontWeight.Bold, fontSize = 10.sp)
                    }
                }
            }

            // Quick Portals Row (Connecting free libraries websites explicitly)
            Column(verticalArrangement = Arrangement.spacedBy(4.dp)) {
                Text("INTEGRATED WEB PLATFORMS:", color = TextMuted, fontSize = 8.sp, fontWeight = FontWeight.Bold)
                Row(
                    modifier = Modifier.fillMaxWidth().horizontalScroll(rememberScrollState()),
                    horizontalArrangement = Arrangement.spacedBy(6.dp)
                ) {
                    val libraries = listOf(
                        "Project Gutenberg" to "https://www.gutenberg.org",
                        "Standard Ebooks" to "https://standardebooks.org",
                        "Open Library" to "https://openlibrary.org",
                        "PDF Drive" to "https://www.pdfdrive.com"
                    )
                    libraries.forEach { (name, url) ->
                        Box(
                            modifier = Modifier
                                .background(Color(0xFF0C101F), RoundedCornerShape(8.dp))
                                .border(1.dp, GridSpace, RoundedCornerShape(8.dp))
                                .clickable {
                                    try {
                                        val intent = android.content.Intent(android.content.Intent.ACTION_VIEW, android.net.Uri.parse(url))
                                        intent.addFlags(android.content.Intent.FLAG_ACTIVITY_NEW_TASK)
                                        context.startActivity(intent)
                                    } catch(e: Exception) {
                                        android.widget.Toast.makeText(context, "Could not open browser", android.widget.Toast.LENGTH_SHORT).show()
                                    }
                                }
                                .padding(horizontal = 10.dp, vertical = 6.dp)
                        ) {
                            Row(verticalAlignment = Alignment.CenterVertically, horizontalArrangement = Arrangement.spacedBy(4.dp)) {
                                Icon(Icons.Default.Language, contentDescription = null, tint = CyberCyan, modifier = Modifier.size(10.dp))
                                Text(name, color = Color.White, fontSize = 9.sp, fontWeight = FontWeight.Bold)
                            }
                        }
                    }
                }
            }

            // Classic Curated Book List
            Text("CLASSIC BESTSELLERS IN LIBRARY:", color = TextMuted, fontSize = 8.sp, fontWeight = FontWeight.Bold)
            LazyRow(
                modifier = Modifier.fillMaxWidth(),
                horizontalArrangement = Arrangement.spacedBy(10.dp)
            ) {
                items(curatedFreeBooks, key = { it.title }) { book ->
                    Column(
                        modifier = Modifier
                            .width(110.dp)
                            .clip(RoundedCornerShape(12.dp))
                            .background(Color(0xFF03070E))
                            .border(1.dp, GridSpace, RoundedCornerShape(12.dp))
                            .clickable { selectedBookForReading = book }
                            .padding(6.dp),
                        verticalArrangement = Arrangement.spacedBy(4.dp)
                    ) {
                        Box(
                            modifier = Modifier
                                .fillMaxWidth()
                                .height(120.dp)
                                .clip(RoundedCornerShape(8.dp))
                                .background(Color.DarkGray)
                        ) {
                            AsyncImage(
                                model = book.coverUrl,
                                contentDescription = null,
                                modifier = Modifier.fillMaxSize(),
                                contentScale = ContentScale.Crop
                            )
                            Box(
                                modifier = Modifier
                                    .align(Alignment.BottomStart)
                                    .padding(4.dp)
                                    .background(CyberPink.copy(alpha = 0.85f), RoundedCornerShape(4.dp))
                                    .padding(horizontal = 4.dp, vertical = 2.dp)
                            ) {
                                Text(book.category, color = Color.Black, fontSize = 7.sp, fontWeight = FontWeight.Bold)
                            }
                        }

                        Text(
                            text = book.title,
                            color = Color.White,
                            fontSize = 10.sp,
                            fontWeight = FontWeight.Bold,
                            maxLines = 1,
                            overflow = TextOverflow.Ellipsis
                        )
                        Text(
                            text = book.author,
                            color = TextMuted,
                            fontSize = 8.sp,
                            maxLines = 1,
                            overflow = TextOverflow.Ellipsis
                        )
                    }
                }
            }
        }
    }

    // E-Book Reader Screen Modal
    if (selectedBookForReading != null) {
        val book = selectedBookForReading!!
        EBookReaderDialog(
            book = book,
            viewModel = viewModel,
            onDismiss = {
                viewModel.stopSpeaking()
                selectedBookForReading = null
            }
        )
    }
}

@Composable
fun EBookReaderDialog(
    book: FreeClassBook,
    viewModel: MainViewModel,
    onDismiss: () -> Unit
) {
    val context = LocalContext.current
    val coroutineScope = rememberCoroutineScope()
    
    var wordSizeMultiplier by remember { mutableStateOf(12) } // default 12sp
    var isReadingTranslation by remember { mutableStateOf(false) }
    var translatedTextHinglish by remember { mutableStateOf("") }
    var isLoadingTranslation by remember { mutableStateOf(false) }
    
    val isTtsActive by viewModel.isTtsActive.collectAsStateWithLifecycle()

    Dialog(
        onDismissRequest = onDismiss,
        properties = androidx.compose.ui.window.DialogProperties(
            usePlatformDefaultWidth = false
        )
    ) {
        Surface(
            modifier = Modifier.fillMaxSize(),
            color = Color(0xFF050814)
        ) {
            Column(modifier = Modifier.fillMaxSize()) {
                // Top Custom Header Controls
                Row(
                    modifier = Modifier
                        .fillMaxWidth()
                        .background(Color(0xFF090D1F))
                        .padding(horizontal = 14.dp, vertical = 12.dp)
                        .border(1.dp, GridSpace, RoundedCornerShape(0.dp)),
                    verticalAlignment = Alignment.CenterVertically,
                    horizontalArrangement = Arrangement.SpaceBetween
                ) {
                    Column(modifier = Modifier.weight(1f)) {
                        Text(book.title, color = Color.White, fontSize = 13.sp, fontWeight = FontWeight.Bold, maxLines = 1, overflow = TextOverflow.Ellipsis)
                        Text("Author: ${book.author}", color = TextMuted, fontSize = 9.sp)
                    }

                    Row(
                        verticalAlignment = Alignment.CenterVertically,
                        horizontalArrangement = Arrangement.spacedBy(8.dp)
                    ) {
                        // Increase font A+
                        IconButton(
                            onClick = { if (wordSizeMultiplier < 22) wordSizeMultiplier += 2 },
                            modifier = Modifier.size(28.dp)
                        ) {
                            Text("A+", color = CyberCyan, fontSize = 11.sp, fontWeight = FontWeight.Bold)
                        }

                        // Decrease font A-
                        IconButton(
                            onClick = { if (wordSizeMultiplier > 8) wordSizeMultiplier -= 2 },
                            modifier = Modifier.size(28.dp)
                        ) {
                            Text("A-", color = CyberCyan, fontSize = 11.sp, fontWeight = FontWeight.Bold)
                        }

                        // Translate Hindi Button
                        IconButton(
                            onClick = {
                                if (!isReadingTranslation) {
                                    if (translatedTextHinglish.isBlank()) {
                                        isLoadingTranslation = true
                                        coroutineScope.launch {
                                            try {
                                                val p = "Directly translate the following book passages into beautiful, extremely clear, simple and complete Hindi/Urdu language script for easy reading. Maintain the exact formatting, dialogue, structure, and chapter details: \n\n${book.textEnglish}"
                                                translatedTextHinglish = viewModel.getLLMResponseForModel(viewModel.selectedModel.value, p)
                                            } catch (e: Exception) {
                                                translatedTextHinglish = "Failed to translate book. Please verify your Gemini connection."
                                            } finally {
                                                isLoadingTranslation = false
                                            }
                                        }
                                    }
                                    isReadingTranslation = true
                                } else {
                                    isReadingTranslation = false
                                }
                            },
                            modifier = Modifier.size(28.dp)
                        ) {
                            Icon(
                                imageVector = Icons.Default.Translate,
                                contentDescription = "Bilingual Hindi Translator",
                                tint = if (isReadingTranslation) CyberPink else Color.White,
                                modifier = Modifier.size(16.dp)
                            )
                        }

                        // TTS Audio speaker
                        IconButton(
                            onClick = {
                                if (isTtsActive) {
                                    viewModel.stopSpeaking()
                                } else {
                                    val textToRead = if (isReadingTranslation && translatedTextHinglish.isNotBlank()) translatedTextHinglish else book.textEnglish
                                    viewModel.generateRealHumanVoiceAndSpeak(
                                        promptText = textToRead.take(4000),
                                        voiceProfile = viewModel.selectedVoiceProfile.value,
                                        languageSelected = if (isReadingTranslation) "Hindi" else "English"
                                    )
                                }
                            },
                            modifier = Modifier.size(28.dp)
                        ) {
                            Icon(
                                imageVector = if (isTtsActive) Icons.Default.VolumeOff else Icons.Default.VolumeUp,
                                contentDescription = "Read Aloud",
                                tint = if (isTtsActive) CyberPink else SuccessGreen,
                                modifier = Modifier.size(16.dp)
                            )
                        }

                        // Browser Link
                        IconButton(
                            onClick = {
                                try {
                                    val intent = android.content.Intent(android.content.Intent.ACTION_VIEW, android.net.Uri.parse(book.sourceUrl))
                                    intent.addFlags(android.content.Intent.FLAG_ACTIVITY_NEW_TASK)
                                    context.startActivity(intent)
                                } catch (e: Exception) {
                                    // silent
                                }
                            },
                            modifier = Modifier.size(28.dp)
                        ) {
                            Icon(Icons.Default.OpenInNew, contentDescription = "Website Source", tint = CyberCyan, modifier = Modifier.size(16.dp))
                        }

                        // Close Dialog
                        IconButton(onClick = onDismiss, modifier = Modifier.size(28.dp)) {
                            Icon(Icons.Default.Close, contentDescription = "Close", tint = TextMuted, modifier = Modifier.size(16.dp))
                        }
                    }
                }

                // Main Reading content
                Box(
                    modifier = Modifier
                        .fillMaxSize()
                        .weight(1f)
                        .padding(14.dp)
                ) {
                    if (isLoadingTranslation) {
                        Column(
                            modifier = Modifier.fillMaxSize(),
                            verticalArrangement = Arrangement.Center,
                            horizontalAlignment = Alignment.CenterHorizontally
                        ) {
                            CircularProgressIndicator(color = CyberPink)
                            Spacer(modifier = Modifier.height(8.dp))
                            Text("Translating full English paragraphs to pristine Hindi text...", color = TextMuted, fontSize = 10.sp)
                        }
                    } else {
                        val displayContent = if (isReadingTranslation) translatedTextHinglish.ifEmpty { "Pristine translated text copy is cooking..." } else book.textEnglish
                        Column(
                            modifier = Modifier
                                .fillMaxSize()
                                .verticalScroll(rememberScrollState())
                        ) {
                            // Mini book info card inside reader
                            Row(
                                modifier = Modifier
                                    .fillMaxWidth()
                                    .background(Color(0xFF0C101F), RoundedCornerShape(12.dp))
                                    .padding(10.dp),
                                horizontalArrangement = Arrangement.spacedBy(10.dp)
                            ) {
                                AsyncImage(
                                    model = book.coverUrl,
                                    contentDescription = null,
                                    modifier = Modifier
                                        .size(44.dp, 64.dp)
                                        .clip(RoundedCornerShape(4.dp)),
                                    contentScale = ContentScale.Crop
                                )
                                Column(verticalArrangement = Arrangement.spacedBy(2.dp)) {
                                    Text(book.title, color = Color.White, fontSize = 11.sp, fontWeight = FontWeight.Bold)
                                    Text(book.description, color = TextMuted, fontSize = 8.sp, maxLines = 3, overflow = TextOverflow.Ellipsis)
                                }
                            }

                            Spacer(modifier = Modifier.height(16.dp))

                            androidx.compose.foundation.text.selection.SelectionContainer {
                                Text(
                                    text = displayContent,
                                    color = if (isReadingTranslation) Color(0xFFE2E8F0) else Color.White,
                                    fontSize = wordSizeMultiplier.sp,
                                    lineHeight = (wordSizeMultiplier + 8).sp,
                                    textAlign = TextAlign.Start,
                                    modifier = Modifier.padding(bottom = 32.dp)
                                )
                            }
                        }
                    }
                }
            }
        }
    }
}

@Composable
fun YouTubeInteractiveWidget(viewModel: MainViewModel) {
    val youtubeVideos by viewModel.youtubeVideos.collectAsStateWithLifecycle()
    val playingVideoId by viewModel.currentPlayingVideoId.collectAsStateWithLifecycle()
    var searchQuery by remember { mutableStateOf("") }
    var isExpanded by remember { mutableStateOf(false) }
    var isVideoFullScreen by remember { mutableStateOf(false) }
    var isYouTubeFullScreenLayout by remember { mutableStateOf(false) }

    val heightDp = if (isExpanded) 490.dp else 290.dp

    // Full Screen Overlaid Dialog for Cinema Mode
    if (isVideoFullScreen && playingVideoId != null) {
        androidx.compose.ui.window.Dialog(
            onDismissRequest = { isVideoFullScreen = false },
            properties = androidx.compose.ui.window.DialogProperties(
                usePlatformDefaultWidth = false
            )
        ) {
            Surface(
                modifier = Modifier.fillMaxSize(),
                color = Color.Black
            ) {
                Box(modifier = Modifier.fillMaxSize()) {
                    AndroidView(
                        factory = { context ->
                            android.webkit.WebView(context).apply {
                                settings.javaScriptEnabled = true
                                settings.domStorageEnabled = true
                                settings.userAgentString = "Mozilla/5.0 (Linux; Android 10; K) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/115.0.0.0 Mobile Safari/537.36"
                                settings.mediaPlaybackRequiresUserGesture = false
                                webChromeClient = android.webkit.WebChromeClient()
                                webViewClient = android.webkit.WebViewClient()
                                tag = playingVideoId
                                
                                val html = """
                                    <!DOCTYPE html>
                                    <html>
                                    <head>
                                    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no">
                                    <style>
                                    body { margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #000000; overflow: hidden; }
                                    .video-container { position: absolute; top:0; left:0; width: 100%; height: 100%; }
                                    .video-container iframe { width: 100%; height: 100%; border: 0; }
                                    </style>
                                    </head>
                                    <body>
                                    <div class="video-container">
                                    <iframe id="player" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/$playingVideoId?autoplay=1&enablejsapi=1&rel=0&playsinline=1" allow="autoplay; encrypted-media; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen></iframe>
                                    </div>
                                    </body>
                                    </html>
                                """.trimIndent()
                                loadDataWithBaseURL("https://www.youtube.com", html, "text/html", "UTF-8", null)
                            }
                        },
                        modifier = Modifier.fillMaxSize()
                    )

                    // Exit Fullscreen Floating Pill
                    Surface(
                        shape = RoundedCornerShape(20.dp),
                        color = Color.Black.copy(alpha = 0.7f),
                        modifier = Modifier
                            .align(Alignment.TopEnd)
                            .padding(16.dp)
                            .clickable { isVideoFullScreen = false }
                            .border(1.dp, Color.White.copy(alpha = 0.4f), RoundedCornerShape(20.dp))
                    ) {
                        Row(
                            verticalAlignment = Alignment.CenterVertically,
                            horizontalArrangement = Arrangement.spacedBy(4.dp),
                            modifier = Modifier.padding(horizontal = 12.dp, vertical = 6.dp)
                        ) {
                            Icon(
                                imageVector = Icons.Default.FullscreenExit,
                                contentDescription = "Close Cinema",
                                tint = Color.White,
                                modifier = Modifier.size(16.dp)
                            )
                            Text("EXIT FULL size", color = Color.White, fontSize = 10.sp, fontWeight = FontWeight.Bold)
                        }
                    }
                }
            }
        }
    }

    if (isYouTubeFullScreenLayout) {
        androidx.compose.ui.window.Dialog(
            onDismissRequest = { isYouTubeFullScreenLayout = false },
            properties = androidx.compose.ui.window.DialogProperties(
                usePlatformDefaultWidth = false
            )
        ) {
            Surface(
                modifier = Modifier.fillMaxSize(),
                color = Color(0xFF070B18)
            ) {
                Column(
                    modifier = Modifier
                        .fillMaxSize()
                        .padding(16.dp),
                    verticalArrangement = Arrangement.spacedBy(12.dp)
                ) {
                    Row(
                        modifier = Modifier.fillMaxWidth(),
                        horizontalArrangement = Arrangement.SpaceBetween,
                        verticalAlignment = Alignment.CenterVertically
                    ) {
                        Row(verticalAlignment = Alignment.CenterVertically, horizontalArrangement = Arrangement.spacedBy(8.dp)) {
                            Text("📺", fontSize = 24.sp)
                            Column {
                                Text("STREAM RABIYA TV (YOUTUBE PRO)", fontWeight = FontWeight.ExtraBold, color = Color.White, fontSize = 14.sp, letterSpacing = 0.5.sp)
                                Text("Fullscreen Cinematic Experience & Scrollable Search Results Active", color = TextMuted, fontSize = 9.sp)
                            }
                        }
                        IconButton(
                            onClick = { isYouTubeFullScreenLayout = false },
                            modifier = Modifier
                                .size(32.dp)
                                .background(GridSpace, CircleShape)
                        ) {
                            Icon(Icons.Default.Close, contentDescription = "Close", tint = Color.White, modifier = Modifier.size(16.dp))
                        }
                    }

                    Divider(color = GridSpace, thickness = 1.dp)

                    playingVideoId?.let { videoId ->
                        Box(
                            modifier = Modifier
                                .fillMaxWidth()
                                .height(220.dp)
                                .background(Color.Black, RoundedCornerShape(16.dp))
                                .clip(RoundedCornerShape(16.dp))
                        ) {
                            AndroidView(
                                factory = { context ->
                                    android.webkit.WebView(context).apply {
                                        settings.javaScriptEnabled = true
                                        settings.domStorageEnabled = true
                                        settings.userAgentString = "Mozilla/5.0 (Linux; Android 10; K) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/115.0.0.0 Mobile Safari/537.36"
                                        settings.mediaPlaybackRequiresUserGesture = false
                                        webChromeClient = android.webkit.WebChromeClient()
                                        webViewClient = android.webkit.WebViewClient()
                                        tag = videoId
                                        
                                        val html = """
                                            <!DOCTYPE html>
                                            <html>
                                            <head>
                                            <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no">
                                            <style>
                                            body { margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #000000; overflow: hidden; }
                                            .video-container { position: relative; padding-bottom: 56.25%; height: 0; overflow: hidden; }
                                            .video-container iframe { position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; border: 0; }
                                            </style>
                                            </head>
                                            <body>
                                            <div class="video-container">
                                            <iframe id="player" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/$videoId?autoplay=1&enablejsapi=1&rel=0&playsinline=1" allow="autoplay; encrypted-media; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen></iframe>
                                            </div>
                                            </body>
                                            </html>
                                        """.trimIndent()
                                        loadDataWithBaseURL("https://www.youtube.com", html, "text/html", "UTF-8", null)
                                    }
                                },
                                update = { webView ->
                                    val currentTag = webView.tag as? String
                                    if (currentTag != videoId) {
                                        webView.tag = videoId
                                        val html = """
                                            <!DOCTYPE html>
                                            <html>
                                            <head>
                                            <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no">
                                            <style>
                                            body { margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #000000; overflow: hidden; }
                                            .video-container { position: relative; padding-bottom: 56.25%; height: 0; overflow: hidden; }
                                            .video-container iframe { position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; border: 0; }
                                            </style>
                                            </head>
                                            <body>
                                            <div class="video-container">
                                            <iframe id="player" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/$videoId?autoplay=1&enablejsapi=1&rel=0&playsinline=1" allow="autoplay; encrypted-media; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen></iframe>
                                            </div>
                                            </body>
                                            </html>
                                        """.trimIndent()
                                        webView.loadDataWithBaseURL("https://www.youtube.com", html, "text/html", "UTF-8", null)
                                    }
                                },
                                modifier = Modifier.fillMaxSize()
                            )
                        }
                    } ?: Box(
                        modifier = Modifier
                            .fillMaxWidth()
                            .height(140.dp)
                            .background(Color.Black, RoundedCornerShape(16.dp)),
                        contentAlignment = Alignment.Center
                    ) {
                        Text("Awaiting video selection...", color = TextMuted, fontSize = 12.sp)
                    }

                    if (playingVideoId != null) {
                        Button(
                            onClick = { isVideoFullScreen = true },
                            colors = ButtonDefaults.buttonColors(containerColor = CyberCyan),
                            shape = RoundedCornerShape(8.dp),
                            modifier = Modifier.fillMaxWidth().height(32.dp)
                        ) {
                            Row(verticalAlignment = Alignment.CenterVertically, horizontalArrangement = Arrangement.spacedBy(6.dp)) {
                                Icon(Icons.Default.Fullscreen, contentDescription = "Full Size", tint = Color.Black, modifier = Modifier.size(16.dp))
                                Text("WATCH IN CINEMA FULL SIZE 🎬", color = Color.Black, fontSize = 10.sp, fontWeight = FontWeight.ExtraBold)
                            }
                        }
                    }

                    Row(
                        modifier = Modifier.fillMaxWidth(),
                        verticalAlignment = Alignment.CenterVertically,
                        horizontalArrangement = Arrangement.spacedBy(8.dp)
                    ) {
                        TextField(
                            value = searchQuery,
                            onValueChange = { searchQuery = it },
                            placeholder = { Text("Search YouTube here...", color = TextMuted, fontSize = 11.sp) },
                            modifier = Modifier
                                .weight(1f)
                                .height(46.dp)
                                .border(1.dp, GridSpace, RoundedCornerShape(10.dp)),
                            colors = TextFieldDefaults.colors(
                                focusedContainerColor = CardSpace,
                                unfocusedContainerColor = CardSpace,
                                focusedIndicatorColor = Color.Transparent,
                                unfocusedIndicatorColor = Color.Transparent,
                                focusedTextColor = Color.White,
                                unfocusedTextColor = Color.White,
                                cursorColor = CyberPink
                            ),
                            singleLine = true,
                            shape = RoundedCornerShape(10.dp)
                        )

                        Button(
                            onClick = {
                                if (searchQuery.isNotBlank()) {
                                    viewModel.searchYouTubeReal(searchQuery)
                                }
                            },
                            colors = ButtonDefaults.buttonColors(containerColor = CyberPink),
                            shape = RoundedCornerShape(10.dp),
                            modifier = Modifier.height(46.dp)
                        ) {
                            Icon(imageVector = Icons.Default.Search, contentDescription = "Search", tint = Color.Black, modifier = Modifier.size(18.dp))
                        }
                    }

                    Text("CHANNELS FEED (${"$"}{youtubeVideos.size} Videos)", color = CyberCyan, fontSize = 9.sp, fontWeight = FontWeight.Bold)

                    LazyColumn(
                        modifier = Modifier
                            .fillMaxWidth()
                            .weight(1f),
                        verticalArrangement = Arrangement.spacedBy(8.dp)
                    ) {
                        items(youtubeVideos, key = { it.id }) { v ->
                            Row(
                                modifier = Modifier
                                    .fillMaxWidth()
                                    .background(Color(0xFF0F172A), RoundedCornerShape(12.dp))
                                    .border(1.dp, if (playingVideoId == v.id) CyberPink else Color.Transparent, RoundedCornerShape(12.dp))
                                    .clickable { viewModel.selectVideoId(v.id) }
                                    .padding(8.dp),
                                verticalAlignment = Alignment.CenterVertically,
                                horizontalArrangement = Arrangement.spacedBy(12.dp)
                            ) {
                                AsyncImage(
                                    model = v.thumbnail,
                                    contentDescription = v.title,
                                    modifier = Modifier
                                        .size(80.dp, 48.dp)
                                        .clip(RoundedCornerShape(8.dp))
                                        .background(Color.Black),
                                    contentScale = ContentScale.Crop
                                )
                                Column(modifier = Modifier.weight(1f)) {
                                    Text(v.title, color = Color.White, fontSize = 11.sp, fontWeight = FontWeight.Bold, maxLines = 2, overflow = TextOverflow.Ellipsis)
                                    Text(v.channel, color = TextMuted, fontSize = 9.sp)
                                }
                                Icon(
                                    imageVector = if (playingVideoId == v.id) Icons.Default.PauseCircle else Icons.Default.PlayCircle,
                                    contentDescription = "Play",
                                    tint = if (playingVideoId == v.id) CyberPink else CyberCyan,
                                    modifier = Modifier.size(24.dp)
                                )
                            }
                        }
                    }
                }
            }
        }
    }

    Surface(
        shape = RoundedCornerShape(24.dp),
        color = Color(0xFF070B18),
        modifier = Modifier
            .fillMaxWidth()
            .height(heightDp)
            .border(1.5.dp, CyberPink.copy(alpha = 0.8f), RoundedCornerShape(24.dp))
            .padding(2.dp)
            .testTag("youtube_interactive_section")
    ) {
        Column(modifier = Modifier.padding(12.dp), verticalArrangement = Arrangement.spacedBy(8.dp)) {
            // Header Row
            Row(
                modifier = Modifier.fillMaxWidth(),
                horizontalArrangement = Arrangement.SpaceBetween,
                verticalAlignment = Alignment.CenterVertically
            ) {
                Row(verticalAlignment = Alignment.CenterVertically, horizontalArrangement = Arrangement.spacedBy(6.dp)) {
                    Text("📺", fontSize = 16.sp)
                    Text("STREAM RABIYA TV (YOUTUBE)", fontWeight = FontWeight.Bold, color = Color.White, fontSize = 11.sp, letterSpacing = 0.5.sp)
                    
                    // Show a Pause pill/button if a video is playing
                    if (playingVideoId != null) {
                        Surface(
                            shape = RoundedCornerShape(12.dp),
                            color = CyberPink.copy(alpha = 0.2f),
                            modifier = Modifier
                                .clickable { viewModel.selectVideoId(null) }
                                .padding(horizontal = 4.dp, vertical = 2.dp)
                                .border(1.dp, CyberPink, RoundedCornerShape(12.dp))
                        ) {
                            Row(
                                verticalAlignment = Alignment.CenterVertically,
                                horizontalArrangement = Arrangement.spacedBy(3.dp),
                                modifier = Modifier.padding(horizontal = 6.dp, vertical = 2.dp)
                            ) {
                                Icon(
                                    imageVector = Icons.Default.Pause,
                                    contentDescription = "Pause",
                                    tint = CyberPink,
                                    modifier = Modifier.size(10.dp)
                                )
                                Text("PAUSE", color = CyberPink, fontSize = 8.sp, fontWeight = FontWeight.Bold)
                            }
                        }

                        Spacer(modifier = Modifier.width(2.dp))

                        // Full size button
                        Surface(
                            shape = RoundedCornerShape(12.dp),
                            color = CyberCyan.copy(alpha = 0.2f),
                            modifier = Modifier
                                .clickable { isVideoFullScreen = true }
                                .padding(horizontal = 4.dp, vertical = 2.dp)
                                .border(1.dp, CyberCyan, RoundedCornerShape(12.dp))
                        ) {
                            Row(
                                verticalAlignment = Alignment.CenterVertically,
                                horizontalArrangement = Arrangement.spacedBy(3.dp),
                                modifier = Modifier.padding(horizontal = 6.dp, vertical = 2.dp)
                            ) {
                                Icon(
                                    imageVector = Icons.Default.Fullscreen,
                                    contentDescription = "Full Size Video",
                                    tint = CyberCyan,
                                    modifier = Modifier.size(10.dp)
                                )
                                Text("FULL size", color = CyberCyan, fontSize = 8.sp, fontWeight = FontWeight.Bold)
                            }
                        }
                    }
                }
                
                Row(verticalAlignment = Alignment.CenterVertically, horizontalArrangement = Arrangement.spacedBy(4.dp)) {
                    // Full Screen layout mode
                    IconButton(
                        onClick = { isYouTubeFullScreenLayout = true },
                        modifier = Modifier.size(24.dp)
                    ) {
                        Icon(
                            imageVector = Icons.Default.AspectRatio,
                            contentDescription = "Full Screen Layout",
                            tint = CyberPink,
                            modifier = Modifier.size(18.dp)
                        )
                    }

                    // Toggle Button to expand video size ("Video badhi karna")
                    IconButton(
                        onClick = { isExpanded = !isExpanded },
                        modifier = Modifier.size(24.dp)
                    ) {
                        Icon(
                            imageVector = if (isExpanded) Icons.Default.FullscreenExit else Icons.Default.Fullscreen,
                            contentDescription = "Resize Screen",
                            tint = CyberCyan,
                            modifier = Modifier.size(18.dp)
                        )
                    }
                }
            }

            val playerHeight = if (isExpanded) 255.dp else 130.dp

            // Real Embedded Player
            playingVideoId?.let { videoId ->
                Box(
                    modifier = Modifier
                        .fillMaxWidth()
                        .height(playerHeight)
                        .background(Color.Black, RoundedCornerShape(12.dp))
                        .clip(RoundedCornerShape(12.dp))
                ) {
                    AndroidView(
                        factory = { context ->
                            android.webkit.WebView(context).apply {
                                settings.javaScriptEnabled = true
                                settings.domStorageEnabled = true
                                settings.userAgentString = "Mozilla/5.0 (Linux; Android 10; K) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/115.0.0.0 Mobile Safari/537.36"
                                settings.mediaPlaybackRequiresUserGesture = false
                                webChromeClient = android.webkit.WebChromeClient()
                                webViewClient = android.webkit.WebViewClient()
                                tag = videoId
                                
                                val html = """
                                    <!DOCTYPE html>
                                    <html>
                                    <head>
                                    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no">
                                    <style>
                                    body { margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #000000; overflow: hidden; }
                                    .video-container { position: relative; padding-bottom: 56.25%; height: 0; overflow: hidden; }
                                    .video-container iframe { position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; border: 0; }
                                    </style>
                                    </head>
                                    <body>
                                    <div class="video-container">
                                    <iframe id="player" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/$videoId?autoplay=1&enablejsapi=1&rel=0&playsinline=1" allow="autoplay; encrypted-media; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen></iframe>
                                    </div>
                                    </body>
                                    </html>
                               RawHTML""".replace("RawHTML", "").trimIndent()
                                loadDataWithBaseURL("https://www.youtube.com", html, "text/html", "UTF-8", null)
                            }
                        },
                        update = { webView ->
                            val currentTag = webView.tag as? String
                            if (currentTag != videoId) {
                                webView.tag = videoId
                                webView.settings.userAgentString = "Mozilla/5.0 (Linux; Android 10; K) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/115.0.0.0 Mobile Safari/537.36"
                                
                                val html = """
                                    <!DOCTYPE html>
                                    <html>
                                    <head>
                                    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no">
                                    <style>
                                    body { margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #000000; overflow: hidden; }
                                    .video-container { position: relative; padding-bottom: 56.25%; height: 0; overflow: hidden; }
                                    .video-container iframe { position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; border: 0; }
                                    </style>
                                    </head>
                                    <body>
                                    <div class="video-container">
                                    <iframe id="player" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/$videoId?autoplay=1&enablejsapi=1&rel=0&playsinline=1" allow="autoplay; encrypted-media; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen></iframe>
                                    </div>
                                    </body>
                                    </html>
                               RawHTML""".replace("RawHTML", "").trimIndent()
                                webView.loadDataWithBaseURL("https://www.youtube.com", html, "text/html", "UTF-8", null)
                             }
                        },
                        modifier = Modifier.fillMaxSize()
                    )
                }
            } ?: Box(
                modifier = Modifier
                    .fillMaxWidth()
                    .height(playerHeight)
                    .background(Color.Black, RoundedCornerShape(12.dp)),
                contentAlignment = Alignment.Center
            ) {
                Text("Select a video from list below", color = TextMuted, fontSize = 11.sp)
            }

            // Search input Row
            Row(
                modifier = Modifier.fillMaxWidth(),
                verticalAlignment = Alignment.CenterVertically,
                horizontalArrangement = Arrangement.spacedBy(6.dp)
            ) {
                TextField(
                    value = searchQuery,
                    onValueChange = { searchQuery = it },
                    placeholder = { Text("Search YouTube here...", color = TextMuted, fontSize = 10.sp) },
                    modifier = Modifier
                        .weight(1f)
                        .height(38.dp)
                        .border(1.dp, GridSpace, RoundedCornerShape(8.dp)),
                    colors = TextFieldDefaults.colors(
                        focusedContainerColor = CardSpace,
                        unfocusedContainerColor = CardSpace,
                        focusedIndicatorColor = Color.Transparent,
                        unfocusedIndicatorColor = Color.Transparent,
                        focusedTextColor = Color.White,
                        unfocusedTextColor = Color.White,
                        cursorColor = CyberPink
                    ),
                    singleLine = true,
                    shape = RoundedCornerShape(8.dp)
                )

                Box(
                    modifier = Modifier
                        .size(34.dp)
                        .background(CyberPink, RoundedCornerShape(8.dp))
                        .clickable {
                            if (searchQuery.isNotBlank()) {
                                viewModel.searchYouTubeReal(searchQuery)
                            }
                        },
                    contentAlignment = Alignment.Center
                ) {
                    Icon(imageVector = Icons.Default.Search, contentDescription = "Search", tint = Color.Black, modifier = Modifier.size(16.dp))
                }
            }

            // Dual Scrollable Video Feed - Horizontal (Compact) vs Vertical (Expanded)
            if (isExpanded) {
                LazyColumn(
                    modifier = Modifier
                        .fillMaxWidth()
                        .weight(1f),
                    verticalArrangement = Arrangement.spacedBy(6.dp)
                ) {
                    items(youtubeVideos, key = { it.id }) { v ->
                        Row(
                            modifier = Modifier
                                .fillMaxWidth()
                                .background(Color(0xFF0F172A), RoundedCornerShape(8.dp))
                                .border(1.dp, if (playingVideoId == v.id) CyberPink else Color.Transparent, RoundedCornerShape(8.dp))
                                .clickable { viewModel.selectVideoId(v.id) }
                                .padding(6.dp),
                            verticalAlignment = Alignment.CenterVertically,
                            horizontalArrangement = Arrangement.spacedBy(8.dp)
                        ) {
                            AsyncImage(
                                model = v.thumbnail,
                                contentDescription = v.title,
                                modifier = Modifier
                                    .size(54.dp, 36.dp)
                                    .clip(RoundedCornerShape(6.dp))
                                    .background(Color.Black),
                                contentScale = ContentScale.Crop
                            )
                            Column(modifier = Modifier.weight(1f)) {
                                Text(v.title, color = Color.White, fontSize = 10.sp, fontWeight = FontWeight.Bold, maxLines = 1, overflow = TextOverflow.Ellipsis)
                                Text(v.channel, color = TextMuted, fontSize = 8.sp, maxLines = 1)
                            }
                            Icon(
                                imageVector = if (playingVideoId == v.id) Icons.Default.PauseCircle else Icons.Default.PlayCircle,
                                contentDescription = "Play",
                                tint = if (playingVideoId == v.id) CyberPink else CyberCyan,
                                modifier = Modifier.size(20.dp)
                            )
                        }
                    }
                }
            } else {
                LazyRow(
                    modifier = Modifier.fillMaxWidth(),
                    horizontalArrangement = Arrangement.spacedBy(6.dp)
                ) {
                    items(youtubeVideos, key = { it.id }) { v ->
                        Row(
                            modifier = Modifier
                                .width(135.dp)
                                .background(Color(0xFF0F172A), RoundedCornerShape(8.dp))
                                .border(1.dp, if (playingVideoId == v.id) CyberPink else Color.Transparent, RoundedCornerShape(8.dp))
                                .clickable { viewModel.selectVideoId(v.id) }
                                .padding(4.dp),
                            verticalAlignment = Alignment.CenterVertically,
                            horizontalArrangement = Arrangement.spacedBy(4.dp)
                        ) {
                            AsyncImage(
                                model = v.thumbnail,
                                contentDescription = v.title,
                                modifier = Modifier
                                    .size(40.dp)
                                    .clip(RoundedCornerShape(4.dp))
                                    .background(Color.Black),
                                contentScale = ContentScale.Crop
                            )
                            Column(modifier = Modifier.weight(1f)) {
                                Text(v.title, color = Color.White, fontSize = 9.sp, fontWeight = FontWeight.Bold, maxLines = 1, overflow = TextOverflow.Ellipsis)
                                Text(v.channel, color = TextMuted, fontSize = 8.sp, maxLines = 1)
                            }
                        }
                    }
                }
            }
        }
    }
}

@Composable
fun MusicPlayerWidget(viewModel: MainViewModel) {
    val context = androidx.compose.ui.platform.LocalContext.current
    val playlist by viewModel.musicPlaylist.collectAsStateWithLifecycle()
    val activeIdx by viewModel.currentTrackIndex.collectAsStateWithLifecycle()
    val isPlaying by viewModel.isMusicPlaying.collectAsStateWithLifecycle()
    val progress by viewModel.musicProgress.collectAsStateWithLifecycle()
    val durationMs by viewModel.musicDurationMs.collectAsStateWithLifecycle()
    val positionMs by viewModel.musicPositionMs.collectAsStateWithLifecycle()

    // Initialize playlist on start
    LaunchedEffect(Unit) {
        viewModel.initializeMusicPlaylist(context)
    }

    val currentTrack = remember(playlist, activeIdx) {
        if (playlist.isNotEmpty() && activeIdx in playlist.indices) playlist[activeIdx] else null
    }

    val formattedDuration = remember(durationMs) {
        val seconds = (durationMs / 1000) % 60
        val minutes = (durationMs / 1000) / 60
        String.format("%02d:%02d", minutes, seconds)
    }

    val formattedPosition = remember(positionMs) {
        val seconds = (positionMs / 1000) % 60
        val minutes = (positionMs / 1000) / 60
        String.format("%02d:%02d", minutes, seconds)
    }

    val infiniteTransition = rememberInfiniteTransition(label = "Cd Spinning")
    val rotAngle by infiniteTransition.animateFloat(
        initialValue = 0f,
        targetValue = 360f,
        animationSpec = infiniteRepeatable(
            animation = tween(4000, easing = androidx.compose.animation.core.LinearEasing),
            repeatMode = androidx.compose.animation.core.RepeatMode.Restart
        ),
        label = "Cd Angle"
    )
    val currentRotation = if (isPlaying) rotAngle else 0f

    var showPlaylist by remember { mutableStateOf(false) }

    Box(
        modifier = Modifier
            .fillMaxWidth()
            .clip(RoundedCornerShape(20.dp))
            .background(CardSpace)
            .border(1.dp, CyberCyan.copy(alpha = 0.2f), RoundedCornerShape(20.dp))
            .padding(16.dp)
    ) {
        Column(verticalArrangement = Arrangement.spacedBy(11.dp)) {
            // Header Row
            Row(
                modifier = Modifier.fillMaxWidth(),
                verticalAlignment = Alignment.CenterVertically,
                horizontalArrangement = Arrangement.SpaceBetween
            ) {
                Row(verticalAlignment = Alignment.CenterVertically) {
                    Icon(
                        imageVector = Icons.Default.MusicNote,
                        contentDescription = null,
                        tint = CyberCyan,
                        modifier = Modifier.size(18.dp)
                    )
                    Spacer(modifier = Modifier.width(6.dp))
                    Text(
                        text = "🎶 CO-COMPANION MUSIC ENGINE",
                        color = CyberCyan,
                        fontSize = 11.sp,
                        fontWeight = FontWeight.ExtraBold,
                        letterSpacing = 0.5.sp
                    )
                }

                Box(
                    modifier = Modifier
                        .background(if (isPlaying) SuccessGreen.copy(alpha = 0.15f) else GridSpace, RoundedCornerShape(6.dp))
                        .padding(horizontal = 8.dp, vertical = 2.dp)
                ) {
                    Text(
                        text = if (isPlaying) "PLAYING LIVE" else "READY",
                        color = if (isPlaying) SuccessGreen else TextMuted,
                        fontSize = 8.sp,
                        fontWeight = FontWeight.Bold
                    )
                }
            }

            // Track Player Main Screen
            Row(
                modifier = Modifier
                    .fillMaxWidth()
                    .background(GridSpace, RoundedCornerShape(12.dp))
                    .padding(12.dp),
                verticalAlignment = Alignment.CenterVertically,
                horizontalArrangement = Arrangement.spacedBy(16.dp)
            ) {
                // Vinyl CD disc graphic
                Box(
                    modifier = Modifier
                        .size(56.dp)
                        .clip(CircleShape)
                        .background(Color.Black)
                        .border(1.5.dp, if (isPlaying) CyberPink else CyberCyan.copy(alpha = 0.5f), CircleShape)
                        .graphicsLayer(rotationZ = currentRotation),
                    contentAlignment = Alignment.Center
                ) {
                    // Outer ridges
                    Box(
                        modifier = Modifier
                            .size(50.dp)
                            .border(1.dp, Color.White.copy(alpha = 0.1f), CircleShape)
                    )
                    Box(
                        modifier = Modifier
                            .size(40.dp)
                            .border(1.dp, Color.White.copy(alpha = 0.15f), CircleShape)
                    )
                    // Inner label with neon accent icon
                    Box(
                        modifier = Modifier
                            .size(24.dp)
                            .background(
                                Brush.radialGradient(listOf(Color(0xFF1E293B), Color.Black))
                            ),
                        contentAlignment = Alignment.Center
                    ) {
                        Icon(
                            imageVector = Icons.Default.Album,
                            contentDescription = null,
                            tint = if (isPlaying) CyberPink else CyberCyan,
                            modifier = Modifier.size(16.dp)
                        )
                    }
                }

                // Title & Details
                Column(modifier = Modifier.weight(1f)) {
                    Text(
                        text = currentTrack?.title ?: "Select Track (Boliye saheli)",
                        color = Color.White,
                        fontSize = 12.sp,
                        fontWeight = FontWeight.Bold,
                        maxLines = 1,
                        overflow = TextOverflow.Ellipsis
                    )
                    Text(
                        text = currentTrack?.artist ?: "Ambient playback",
                        color = TextMuted,
                        fontSize = 9.sp,
                        maxLines = 1,
                        overflow = TextOverflow.Ellipsis
                    )
                    Text(
                        text = if (currentTrack?.isLocal == true) "💾 LOCAL STORAGE SOURCE" else "🌐 HIGH QUALITY STREAM",
                        color = if (currentTrack?.isLocal == true) CyberPink else CyberCyan,
                        fontSize = 8.sp,
                        fontWeight = FontWeight.SemiBold,
                        letterSpacing = 0.5.sp,
                        modifier = Modifier.padding(top = 2.dp)
                    )
                }
            }

            // Stream progress seek bar
            Column(verticalArrangement = Arrangement.spacedBy(2.dp)) {
                // Time markers
                Row(
                    modifier = Modifier.fillMaxWidth(),
                    horizontalArrangement = Arrangement.SpaceBetween,
                    verticalAlignment = Alignment.CenterVertically
                ) {
                    Text(text = formattedPosition, color = TextMuted, fontSize = 9.sp)
                    Text(text = formattedDuration, color = TextMuted, fontSize = 9.sp)
                }

                // Interactive slider
                Slider(
                    value = progress,
                    onValueChange = { viewModel.seekMusicTo(it) },
                    colors = SliderDefaults.colors(
                        activeTrackColor = CyberCyan,
                        inactiveTrackColor = GridSpace,
                        thumbColor = CyberPink
                    ),
                    modifier = Modifier
                        .fillMaxWidth()
                        .height(18.dp)
                )
            }

            // Audio Player controls
            Row(
                modifier = Modifier.fillMaxWidth(),
                horizontalArrangement = Arrangement.SpaceEvenly,
                verticalAlignment = Alignment.CenterVertically
            ) {
                // Collapsible Playlist trigger
                IconButton(
                    onClick = { showPlaylist = !showPlaylist },
                    modifier = Modifier.size(36.dp)
                ) {
                    Icon(
                        imageVector = if (showPlaylist) Icons.Default.QueueMusic else Icons.Default.FormatListBulleted,
                        contentDescription = "Playlist",
                        tint = if (showPlaylist) CyberCyan else TextLight,
                        modifier = Modifier.size(18.dp)
                    )
                }

                // Prev
                IconButton(
                    onClick = { viewModel.prevMusicTrack(context) },
                    modifier = Modifier
                        .size(36.dp)
                        .background(GridSpace, CircleShape)
                ) {
                    Icon(
                        imageVector = Icons.Default.SkipPrevious,
                        contentDescription = "Previous",
                        tint = Color.White,
                        modifier = Modifier.size(18.dp)
                    )
                }

                // Play / Pause Circle
                Box(
                    modifier = Modifier
                        .size(46.dp)
                        .clip(CircleShape)
                        .background(
                            Brush.linearGradient(listOf(CyberPink, Color(0xFFC084FC)))
                        )
                        .clickable { viewModel.toggleMusicPlayPause(context) },
                    contentAlignment = Alignment.Center
                ) {
                    Icon(
                        imageVector = if (isPlaying) Icons.Default.Pause else Icons.Default.PlayArrow,
                        contentDescription = "Play/Pause",
                        tint = Color.Black,
                        modifier = Modifier.size(24.dp)
                    )
                }

                // Next
                IconButton(
                    onClick = { viewModel.nextMusicTrack(context) },
                    modifier = Modifier
                        .size(36.dp)
                        .background(GridSpace, CircleShape)
                ) {
                    Icon(
                        imageVector = Icons.Default.SkipNext,
                        contentDescription = "Next",
                        tint = Color.White,
                        modifier = Modifier.size(18.dp)
                    )
                }

                // Stop
                IconButton(
                    onClick = { viewModel.stopMusic() },
                    modifier = Modifier
                        .size(36.dp)
                        .background(GridSpace, CircleShape)
                ) {
                    Icon(
                        imageVector = Icons.Default.Stop,
                        contentDescription = "Stop",
                        tint = CyberPink,
                        modifier = Modifier.size(16.dp)
                    )
                }
            }

            // Embedded Expandable Tracks List panel
            if (showPlaylist) {
                Divider(color = GridSpace, thickness = 1.dp, modifier = Modifier.padding(top = 4.dp))
                
                Text(
                    text = "AVAILABLE SONGS PLAYLIST (${playlist.size})",
                    color = TextMuted,
                    fontSize = 9.sp,
                    fontWeight = FontWeight.Bold,
                    letterSpacing = 0.5.sp,
                    modifier = Modifier.padding(start = 2.dp, bottom = 4.dp)
                )

                Column(
                    verticalArrangement = Arrangement.spacedBy(6.dp),
                    modifier = Modifier.fillMaxWidth()
                ) {
                    playlist.forEachIndexed { idx, track ->
                        val isCurrent = idx == activeIdx
                        Row(
                            modifier = Modifier
                                .fillMaxWidth()
                                .clip(RoundedCornerShape(8.dp))
                                .background(if (isCurrent) GridSpace else Color.Transparent)
                                .clickable { viewModel.playMusicMatchIndex(context, idx) }
                                .padding(8.dp),
                            verticalAlignment = Alignment.CenterVertically,
                            horizontalArrangement = Arrangement.SpaceBetween
                        ) {
                            Row(
                                verticalAlignment = Alignment.CenterVertically,
                                horizontalArrangement = Arrangement.spacedBy(10.dp),
                                modifier = Modifier.weight(1f)
                            ) {
                                Icon(
                                    imageVector = if (isCurrent && isPlaying) Icons.Filled.VolumeUp else Icons.Default.MusicNote,
                                    contentDescription = null,
                                    tint = if (isCurrent) CyberPink else TextMuted,
                                    modifier = Modifier.size(14.dp)
                                )

                                Column {
                                    Text(
                                        text = track.title,
                                        color = if (isCurrent) CyberCyan else Color.White,
                                        fontSize = 11.sp,
                                        fontWeight = if (isCurrent) FontWeight.Bold else FontWeight.Medium,
                                        maxLines = 1,
                                        overflow = TextOverflow.Ellipsis
                                    )
                                    Text(
                                        text = track.artist,
                                        color = TextMuted,
                                        fontSize = 9.sp,
                                        maxLines = 1,
                                        overflow = TextOverflow.Ellipsis
                                    )
                                }
                            }
                            
                            Box(
                                modifier = Modifier
                                    .background(if (track.isLocal) CyberPink.copy(alpha = 0.15f) else CyberCyan.copy(alpha = 0.15f), RoundedCornerShape(4.dp))
                                    .padding(horizontal = 4.dp, vertical = 2.dp)
                            ) {
                                Text(
                                    text = if (track.isLocal) "LOCAL" else "WEB",
                                    color = if (track.isLocal) CyberPink else CyberCyan,
                                    fontSize = 7.sp,
                                    fontWeight = FontWeight.Black
                                )
                            }
                        }
                    }
                }
            }
        }
    }
}

@Composable
fun WorkspaceToolButton(
    title: String,
    desc: String,
    action: String,
    onClick: () -> Unit
) {
    val icon = when (action) {
        "google_news" -> Icons.Default.Newspaper
        "keywords_research" -> Icons.Default.Search
        "excel_notepait" -> Icons.Default.TableChart
        "paint_sketch" -> Icons.Default.Brush
        "website_analysis" -> Icons.Default.Web
        "domain_authority" -> Icons.Default.VerifiedUser
        "website_traffic" -> Icons.Default.TrendingUp
        "yt_title" -> Icons.Default.OndemandVideo
        "yt_keywords" -> Icons.Default.Label
        "code_explorer" -> Icons.Default.Code
        "google_maps_tool" -> Icons.Default.Map
        "google_tools_hub" -> Icons.Default.Apps
        else -> Icons.Default.Build
    }
    val color = when (action) {
        "google_news" -> Color(0xFF4285F4)
        "keywords_research" -> Color(0xFFFFB300)
        "excel_notepait" -> Color(0xFF107C41)
        "paint_sketch" -> CyberPink
        "website_analysis" -> CyberCyan
        "domain_authority" -> Color(0xFF7B1FA2)
        "website_traffic" -> Color(0xFF00ACC1)
        "yt_title" -> Color(0xFFE53935)
        "yt_keywords" -> Color(0xFFD81B60)
        "code_explorer" -> Color(0xFF6366F1)
        "google_maps_tool" -> Color(0xFFEA4335)
        "google_tools_hub" -> Color(0xFF4285F4)
        else -> CyberCyan
    }

    Box(
        modifier = Modifier
            .fillMaxWidth()
            .height(84.dp)
            .background(Color(0xFF090D1A), RoundedCornerShape(14.dp))
            .border(1.dp, Color(0xFF1E293B), RoundedCornerShape(14.dp))
            .clickable(onClick = onClick)
            .padding(8.dp)
    ) {
        Column(
            modifier = Modifier.fillMaxSize(),
            verticalArrangement = Arrangement.SpaceBetween,
            horizontalAlignment = Alignment.CenterHorizontally
        ) {
            Box(
                modifier = Modifier
                    .size(28.dp)
                    .background(color.copy(alpha = 0.15f), CircleShape)
                    .border(0.8.dp, color.copy(alpha = 0.4f), CircleShape),
                contentAlignment = Alignment.Center
            ) {
                Icon(imageVector = icon, contentDescription = title, tint = color, modifier = Modifier.size(13.dp))
            }
            Column(horizontalAlignment = Alignment.CenterHorizontally) {
                Text(
                    text = title,
                    color = Color.White,
                    fontSize = 8.5.sp,
                    fontWeight = FontWeight.Bold,
                    maxLines = 1,
                    textAlign = androidx.compose.ui.text.style.TextAlign.Center
                )
                Text(
                    text = desc,
                    color = TextMuted,
                    fontSize = 7.sp,
                    maxLines = 1,
                    textAlign = androidx.compose.ui.text.style.TextAlign.Center
                )
            }
        }
    }
}

@Composable
fun HomeWorkspaceDialog(
    action: String,
    viewModel: MainViewModel,
    onDismiss: () -> Unit
) {
    val context = LocalContext.current
    val coroutineScope = rememberCoroutineScope()
    var isFullScreen by remember { mutableStateOf(true) }

    Dialog(
        onDismissRequest = onDismiss,
        properties = androidx.compose.ui.window.DialogProperties(
            usePlatformDefaultWidth = false
        )
    ) {
        Surface(
            shape = if (isFullScreen) RoundedCornerShape(0.dp) else RoundedCornerShape(24.dp),
            color = Color(0xFF090D1A),
            modifier = if (isFullScreen) {
                Modifier.fillMaxSize()
            } else {
                Modifier
                    .fillMaxWidth()
                    .height(640.dp)
                    .padding(8.dp)
            }
            .border(
                1.5.dp, 
                CyberCyan, 
                if (isFullScreen) RoundedCornerShape(0.dp) else RoundedCornerShape(24.dp)
            )
        ) {
            Column(
                modifier = Modifier
                    .fillMaxSize()
                    .padding(16.dp),
                verticalArrangement = Arrangement.spacedBy(14.dp)
            ) {
                // Shared Top Row
                Row(
                    modifier = Modifier.fillMaxWidth(),
                    horizontalArrangement = Arrangement.SpaceBetween,
                    verticalAlignment = Alignment.CenterVertically
                ) {
                    val dialogTitle = when (action) {
                        "google_news" -> "📰 GOOGLE NEWS ANALYZER"
                        "keywords_research" -> "🔍 GOOGLE SEO KEYWORDS LAB"
                        "excel_notepait" -> "📊 EXCEL SHEET & NOTEPAD"
                        "paint_sketch" -> "🎨 INTUITIVE PAINT SKETCH"
                        "website_analysis" -> "🌐 WEBSITE AUDIT STATION"
                        "domain_authority" -> "🛡️ DOMAIN AUTHORITY TELEMETRY"
                        "website_traffic" -> "📈 TRAFFIC INTELLIGENCE"
                        "yt_title" -> "🎬 VIRAL YT TITLE HACKS"
                        "yt_keywords" -> "🏷️ YT SEO KEYWORDS TARGET"
                        "code_explorer" -> "💻 CODE EXPLORER SANDBOX"
                        "google_maps_tool" -> "🗺️ GOOGLE MAPS PRO & NAVIGATION"
                        "google_tools_hub" -> "🚀 GOOGLE WORKSPACE ECOSYSTEM"
                        else -> "⚙️ DIGITAL WORKSPACE"
                    }
                    Text(
                        text = dialogTitle,
                        fontWeight = FontWeight.ExtraBold,
                        color = Color.White,
                        fontSize = 13.sp,
                        letterSpacing = 0.8.sp
                    )
                    Row(
                        verticalAlignment = Alignment.CenterVertically,
                        horizontalArrangement = Arrangement.spacedBy(8.dp)
                    ) {
                        IconButton(onClick = { isFullScreen = !isFullScreen }, modifier = Modifier.size(24.dp)) {
                            Icon(
                                imageVector = if (isFullScreen) Icons.Default.FullscreenExit else Icons.Default.Fullscreen,
                                contentDescription = "Toggle Fullscreen",
                                tint = CyberCyan,
                                modifier = Modifier.size(18.dp)
                            )
                        }
                        IconButton(onClick = onDismiss, modifier = Modifier.size(24.dp)) {
                            Icon(Icons.Default.Close, contentDescription = "Close", tint = TextMuted, modifier = Modifier.size(16.dp))
                        }
                    }
                }

                Divider(color = GridSpace, thickness = 1.dp)

                // Render specific layout inside a weighable box
                Box(modifier = Modifier.weight(1f)) {
                    when (action) {
                        "google_news" -> {
                            var keyword by remember { mutableStateOf("Tech & Artificial Intelligence") }
                            val liveArticles by viewModel.googleNewsArticles.collectAsStateWithLifecycle()
                            var isFetchingNews by remember { mutableStateOf(false) }

                            // Immersive News Reader States
                            var readingArticle by remember { mutableStateOf<com.example.NewsArticle?>(null) }
                            var isGeneratingDraft by remember { mutableStateOf(false) }
                            var simulatedDraftText by remember { mutableStateOf("") }

                            LaunchedEffect(keyword) {
                                if (liveArticles.isEmpty()) {
                                    viewModel.fetchGoogleNewsReal(keyword)
                                }
                            }

                            if (readingArticle != null) {
                                Column(
                                    modifier = Modifier
                                        .fillMaxSize()
                                        .verticalScroll(rememberScrollState()),
                                    verticalArrangement = Arrangement.spacedBy(16.dp)
                                ) {
                                    Row(
                                        modifier = Modifier.fillMaxWidth(),
                                        horizontalArrangement = Arrangement.SpaceBetween,
                                        verticalAlignment = Alignment.CenterVertically
                                    ) {
                                        TextButton(onClick = { readingArticle = null }) {
                                            Row(verticalAlignment = Alignment.CenterVertically) {
                                                Icon(Icons.Default.ArrowBack, contentDescription = null, tint = CyberCyan, modifier = Modifier.size(16.dp))
                                                Spacer(modifier = Modifier.width(4.dp))
                                                Text("BACK TO LIST", color = CyberCyan, fontWeight = FontWeight.Bold, fontSize = 11.sp)
                                            }
                                        }

                                        Row(horizontalArrangement = Arrangement.spacedBy(8.dp)) {
                                            IconButton(onClick = {
                                                try {
                                                    val intent = android.content.Intent(android.content.Intent.ACTION_VIEW, android.net.Uri.parse(readingArticle!!.link))
                                                    intent.addFlags(android.content.Intent.FLAG_ACTIVITY_NEW_TASK)
                                                    context.startActivity(intent)
                                                } catch(ex: Exception) {
                                                    // silent
                                                }
                                            }, modifier = Modifier.size(32.dp)) {
                                                Icon(Icons.Default.Language, contentDescription = "Open Web URL", tint = CyberCyan, modifier = Modifier.size(18.dp))
                                            }

                                            IconButton(onClick = {
                                                coroutineScope.launch {
                                                    val speechText = if (simulatedDraftText.isNotBlank()) simulatedDraftText else readingArticle!!.title
                                                    viewModel.generateRealHumanVoiceAndSpeak(speechText, viewModel.selectedVoiceProfile.value, "Hindi")
                                                }
                                            }, modifier = Modifier.size(32.dp)) {
                                                Icon(Icons.Default.VolumeUp, contentDescription = "Listen", tint = CyberPink, modifier = Modifier.size(18.dp))
                                            }
                                        }
                                    }

                                    Box(
                                        modifier = Modifier
                                            .fillMaxWidth()
                                            .height(200.dp)
                                            .clip(RoundedCornerShape(16.dp))
                                            .border(1.dp, CyberCyan.copy(alpha = 0.3f), RoundedCornerShape(16.dp))
                                    ) {
                                        AsyncImage(
                                            model = readingArticle!!.imageUrl,
                                            contentDescription = null,
                                            modifier = Modifier.fillMaxSize(),
                                            contentScale = androidx.compose.ui.layout.ContentScale.Crop
                                        )
                                        Box(
                                            modifier = Modifier
                                                .fillMaxSize()
                                                .background(
                                                    androidx.compose.ui.graphics.Brush.verticalGradient(
                                                        listOf(Color.Transparent, Color.Black.copy(alpha = 0.8f))
                                                    )
                                                )
                                        )
                                        Box(
                                            modifier = Modifier
                                                .align(Alignment.TopEnd)
                                                .padding(12.dp)
                                                .background(CyberPink.copy(alpha = 0.85f), RoundedCornerShape(6.dp))
                                                .padding(horizontal = 8.dp, vertical = 4.dp)
                                        ) {
                                            Text("LIVE INTEL", color = Color.Black, fontSize = 8.sp, fontWeight = FontWeight.Bold)
                                        }
                                    }

                                    Column(verticalArrangement = Arrangement.spacedBy(4.dp)) {
                                        Row(
                                            verticalAlignment = Alignment.CenterVertically,
                                            horizontalArrangement = Arrangement.spacedBy(8.dp)
                                        ) {
                                            Box(
                                                modifier = Modifier
                                                    .background(CyberCyan.copy(alpha = 0.15f), RoundedCornerShape(4.dp))
                                                    .padding(horizontal = 6.dp, vertical = 2.dp)
                                            ) {
                                                Text(readingArticle!!.source, color = CyberCyan, fontSize = 9.sp, fontWeight = FontWeight.Bold)
                                            }
                                            Text(
                                                text = readingArticle!!.pubDate.substringBefore(" +") ?: readingArticle!!.pubDate,
                                                color = TextMuted,
                                                fontSize = 9.sp,
                                                fontWeight = FontWeight.Medium
                                            )
                                        }
                                        Text(
                                            text = readingArticle!!.title,
                                            color = Color.White,
                                            fontSize = 15.sp,
                                            fontWeight = FontWeight.ExtraBold,
                                            lineHeight = 22.sp
                                        )
                                    }

                                    Divider(color = GridSpace, thickness = 1.dp)

                                    if (isGeneratingDraft) {
                                        Column(
                                            modifier = Modifier.fillMaxWidth().padding(vertical = 40.dp),
                                            horizontalAlignment = Alignment.CenterHorizontally,
                                            verticalArrangement = Arrangement.spacedBy(10.dp)
                                        ) {
                                            CircularProgressIndicator(color = CyberCyan, modifier = Modifier.size(24.dp))
                                            Text("Generating full-length article details...", color = TextMuted, fontSize = 10.sp)
                                        }
                                    } else {
                                        Text(
                                            text = simulatedDraftText,
                                            color = TextLight,
                                            fontSize = 12.sp,
                                            lineHeight = 20.sp,
                                            modifier = Modifier.padding(bottom = 24.dp)
                                        )
                                    }
                                }
                            } else {
                                Column(
                                    modifier = Modifier.fillMaxSize(),
                                    verticalArrangement = Arrangement.spacedBy(10.dp)
                                ) {
                                    Text("Real-time Google News Live Intel Stream:", color = TextLight, fontSize = 11.sp, fontWeight = FontWeight.Bold)
                                    Row(
                                        modifier = Modifier.fillMaxWidth(),
                                        verticalAlignment = Alignment.CenterVertically,
                                        horizontalArrangement = Arrangement.spacedBy(6.dp)
                                    ) {
                                        OutlinedTextField(
                                            value = keyword,
                                            onValueChange = { keyword = it },
                                            modifier = Modifier.weight(1f),
                                            colors = OutlinedTextFieldDefaults.colors(
                                                focusedTextColor = Color.White,
                                                unfocusedTextColor = Color.White,
                                                focusedBorderColor = CyberCyan,
                                                unfocusedBorderColor = GridSpace
                                            ),
                                            placeholder = { Text("Search any Google News topic...", color = TextMuted, fontSize = 11.sp) },
                                            singleLine = true
                                        )

                                        Button(
                                            onClick = {
                                                isFetchingNews = true
                                                coroutineScope.launch {
                                                    viewModel.fetchGoogleNewsReal(keyword)
                                                    isFetchingNews = false
                                                }
                                            },
                                            colors = ButtonDefaults.buttonColors(containerColor = CyberCyan),
                                            shape = RoundedCornerShape(10.dp),
                                            contentPadding = PaddingValues(horizontal = 12.dp)
                                        ) {
                                            if (isFetchingNews) {
                                                CircularProgressIndicator(color = Color.Black, modifier = Modifier.size(14.dp), strokeWidth = 2.dp)
                                            } else {
                                                Text("SEARCH", color = Color.Black, fontWeight = FontWeight.Bold, fontSize = 10.sp)
                                            }
                                        }
                                    }

                                    Row(
                                        modifier = Modifier.fillMaxWidth(),
                                        horizontalArrangement = Arrangement.SpaceBetween,
                                        verticalAlignment = Alignment.CenterVertically
                                    ) {
                                        Text("Fetched Google News Articles:", fontSize = 10.sp, color = TextMuted)
                                        
                                        Button(
                                            onClick = {
                                                coroutineScope.launch {
                                                    if (liveArticles.isNotEmpty()) {
                                                        val headlines = liveArticles.take(4).joinToString(". ") { it.title }
                                                        val speakPrompt = "Summarize these real news headlines in 2 sweet short Urdu/Hindi sentences to read aloud to the user: $headlines"
                                                        val summaryText = viewModel.getLLMResponseForModel(viewModel.selectedModel.value, speakPrompt)
                                                        viewModel.generateRealHumanVoiceAndSpeak(summaryText, viewModel.selectedVoiceProfile.value, "Hindi")
                                                    } else {
                                                        viewModel.generateRealHumanVoiceAndSpeak("Abhi tak koi news load nahi hui hai. Search button dabayein.", viewModel.selectedVoiceProfile.value, "Hindi")
                                                    }
                                                }
                                            },
                                            colors = ButtonDefaults.buttonColors(containerColor = CyberPink),
                                            shape = RoundedCornerShape(8.dp),
                                            contentPadding = PaddingValues(horizontal = 8.dp, vertical = 2.dp),
                                            modifier = Modifier.height(26.dp)
                                        ) {
                                            Row(verticalAlignment = Alignment.CenterVertically, horizontalArrangement = Arrangement.spacedBy(4.dp)) {
                                                Icon(Icons.Default.VolumeUp, contentDescription = "Listen", tint = Color.Black, modifier = Modifier.size(12.dp))
                                                Text("RABIYA LIVE BROADCAST 🗣️", color = Color.Black, fontSize = 9.sp, fontWeight = FontWeight.ExtraBold)
                                            }
                                        }
                                    }

                                    Column(
                                        modifier = Modifier
                                            .weight(1f)
                                            .verticalScroll(rememberScrollState()),
                                        verticalArrangement = Arrangement.spacedBy(8.dp)
                                    ) {
                                        if (liveArticles.isEmpty()) {
                                            Box(
                                                modifier = Modifier.fillMaxWidth().height(120.dp),
                                                contentAlignment = Alignment.Center
                                            ) {
                                                Text("No live news headlines loaded. Try searching for other topic.", color = TextMuted, fontSize = 11.sp)
                                            }
                                        } else {
                                            liveArticles.take(12).forEachIndexed { index, art ->
                                                Box(
                                                    modifier = Modifier
                                                        .fillMaxWidth()
                                                        .clip(RoundedCornerShape(12.dp))
                                                        .background(Color(0xFF03070E))
                                                        .border(1.dp, GridSpace, RoundedCornerShape(12.dp))
                                                        .clickable {
                                                            readingArticle = art
                                                            isGeneratingDraft = true
                                                            simulatedDraftText = ""
                                                            coroutineScope.launch {
                                                                try {
                                                                    val p = "Generate a highly detailed full news story based on typical journalism standards in Hindi for: '${art.title}' from '${art.source}'. Format with clean reading paragraphs and double linebreaks. Provide a deeply satisfying read of 3-4 paragraphs."
                                                                    val reply = viewModel.getLLMResponseForModel(viewModel.selectedModel.value, p)
                                                                    simulatedDraftText = reply
                                                                } catch(e: Exception) {
                                                                    simulatedDraftText = "Original Headline: ${art.title}\n\nFailed to download entire live article dynamically. Please verify internet connectivity or tap on standard browser link."
                                                                } finally {
                                                                    isGeneratingDraft = false
                                                                }
                                                            }
                                                        }
                                                        .padding(10.dp)
                                                ) {
                                                    Row(
                                                        modifier = Modifier.fillMaxWidth(),
                                                        horizontalArrangement = Arrangement.spacedBy(10.dp),
                                                        verticalAlignment = Alignment.CenterVertically
                                                    ) {
                                                        Box(
                                                            modifier = Modifier
                                                                .size(64.dp)
                                                                .clip(RoundedCornerShape(8.dp))
                                                                .border(1.dp, GridSpace, RoundedCornerShape(8.dp))
                                                        ) {
                                                            AsyncImage(
                                                                model = art.imageUrl,
                                                                contentDescription = null,
                                                                modifier = Modifier.fillMaxSize(),
                                                                contentScale = androidx.compose.ui.layout.ContentScale.Crop
                                                            )
                                                        }

                                                        Column(modifier = Modifier.weight(1f)) {
                                                            Text(art.title, color = Color.White, fontSize = 11.sp, fontWeight = FontWeight.Bold, maxLines = 2, overflow = TextOverflow.Ellipsis)
                                                            Spacer(modifier = Modifier.height(4.dp))
                                                            Row(
                                                                horizontalArrangement = Arrangement.spacedBy(6.dp),
                                                                verticalAlignment = Alignment.CenterVertically
                                                            ) {
                                                                Text(art.source, color = CyberCyan, fontSize = 9.sp, fontWeight = FontWeight.Bold)
                                                                Text("•", color = TextMuted, fontSize = 8.sp)
                                                                Text(art.pubDate.substringBefore(" +") ?: art.pubDate, color = TextMuted, fontSize = 9.sp)
                                                            }
                                                        }

                                                        IconButton(
                                                            onClick = {
                                                                coroutineScope.launch {
                                                                    val intro = "Suniye ye khabar: ${art.title}."
                                                                    viewModel.generateRealHumanVoiceAndSpeak(intro, viewModel.selectedVoiceProfile.value, "Hindi")
                                                                }
                                                            },
                                                            modifier = Modifier.size(28.dp)
                                                        ) {
                                                            Icon(Icons.Default.VolumeUp, contentDescription = "Play News", tint = CyberCyan, modifier = Modifier.size(16.dp))
                                                        }
                                                    }
                                                }
                                            }
                                        }
                                    }
                                }
                            }
                        }

                        "keywords_research" -> {
                            var seed by remember { mutableStateOf("android app") }
                            var region by remember { mutableStateOf("Global") }
                            var isLoading by remember { mutableStateOf(false) }
                            var researchResult by remember { mutableStateOf("") }

                            Column(
                                modifier = Modifier.fillMaxSize(),
                                verticalArrangement = Arrangement.spacedBy(10.dp)
                            ) {
                                Text("Seed Keyword:", color = TextLight, fontSize = 11.sp)
                                OutlinedTextField(
                                    value = seed,
                                    onValueChange = { seed = it },
                                    modifier = Modifier.fillMaxWidth(),
                                    colors = OutlinedTextFieldDefaults.colors(
                                        focusedTextColor = Color.White,
                                        unfocusedTextColor = Color.White,
                                        focusedBorderColor = CyberCyan,
                                        unfocusedBorderColor = GridSpace
                                    ),
                                    singleLine = true
                                )

                                Text("Target Region Focus:", color = TextLight, fontSize = 11.sp)
                                Row(
                                    modifier = Modifier.fillMaxWidth(),
                                    horizontalArrangement = Arrangement.spacedBy(6.dp)
                                ) {
                                    listOf("Global", "India", "UK/US", "Canada").forEach { r ->
                                        Box(
                                            modifier = Modifier
                                                .background(if (region == r) CyberCyan.copy(alpha = 0.2f) else GridSpace, RoundedCornerShape(8.dp))
                                                .border(1.dp, if (region == r) CyberCyan else Color.Transparent, RoundedCornerShape(8.dp))
                                                .clickable { region = r }
                                                .padding(horizontal = 12.dp, vertical = 6.dp)
                                        ) {
                                            Text(r, color = if (region == r) CyberCyan else Color.White, fontSize = 10.sp, fontWeight = FontWeight.Bold)
                                        }
                                    }
                                }

                                Button(
                                    onClick = {
                                        isLoading = true
                                        coroutineScope.launch {
                                            val prompt = "Act as an expert SEO planner. Generate a highly detailed competitive keywords research report for the seed keyword '$seed' under the region focus '$region'. Include Search Intent, Search Volume, CPC, Difficulty (KD %), and an advice checklist. Format as a neat text table."
                                            val reply = viewModel.getLLMResponseForModel(viewModel.selectedModel.value, prompt)
                                            researchResult = reply
                                            viewModel.addFileToFileManager(context, "Keywords_SEO_${System.currentTimeMillis()}.txt", "Documents", "SEED: $seed\nREGION: $region\n\n$reply")
                                            isLoading = false
                                        }
                                    },
                                    colors = ButtonDefaults.buttonColors(containerColor = CyberCyan),
                                    modifier = Modifier.fillMaxWidth(),
                                    shape = RoundedCornerShape(10.dp),
                                    enabled = !isLoading
                                ) {
                                    if (isLoading) {
                                        CircularProgressIndicator(color = Color.Black, modifier = Modifier.size(16.dp), strokeWidth = 2.dp)
                                    } else {
                                        Text("ANALYZE SEO METRICS 🔎", color = Color.Black, fontWeight = FontWeight.Bold, fontSize = 11.sp)
                                    }
                                }

                                if (researchResult.isNotEmpty()) {
                                    Column(
                                        modifier = Modifier
                                            .fillMaxSize()
                                            .background(Color(0xFF03070E), RoundedCornerShape(12.dp))
                                            .border(1.dp, GridSpace, RoundedCornerShape(12.dp))
                                            .verticalScroll(rememberScrollState())
                                            .padding(14.dp),
                                        verticalArrangement = Arrangement.spacedBy(8.dp)
                                    ) {
                                        Text("Keyword Audit Overview:", color = CyberPink, fontWeight = FontWeight.Bold, fontSize = 12.sp)
                                        Text(researchResult, color = Color.White, fontSize = 11.sp, lineHeight = 16.sp)
                                        Text("📁 Keyword report successfully wrote to local files (Documents)!", color = SuccessGreen, fontSize = 9.sp, fontWeight = FontWeight.SemiBold)
                                    }
                                }
                            }
                        }

                        "excel_notepait" -> {
                            var activeTab by remember { mutableStateOf(0) } // 0: Excel Csv Creator, 1: Notepad Draft

                            Column(
                                modifier = Modifier.fillMaxSize(),
                                verticalArrangement = Arrangement.spacedBy(10.dp)
                            ) {
                                // Nested tabs selector
                                Row(
                                    modifier = Modifier
                                        .fillMaxWidth()
                                        .background(GridSpace, RoundedCornerShape(10.dp))
                                        .padding(4.dp)
                                ) {
                                    Box(
                                        modifier = Modifier
                                            .weight(1f)
                                            .background(if (activeTab == 0) Color(0xFF0C101F) else Color.Transparent, RoundedCornerShape(8.dp))
                                            .clickable { activeTab = 0 }
                                            .padding(vertical = 6.dp),
                                        contentAlignment = Alignment.Center
                                    ) {
                                        Text("📊 EXCEL CSV SHEET", color = if (activeTab == 0) CyberCyan else Color.White, fontSize = 10.sp, fontWeight = FontWeight.Bold)
                                    }
                                    Box(
                                        modifier = Modifier
                                            .weight(1f)
                                            .background(if (activeTab == 1) Color(0xFF0C101F) else Color.Transparent, RoundedCornerShape(8.dp))
                                            .clickable { activeTab = 1 }
                                            .padding(vertical = 6.dp),
                                        contentAlignment = Alignment.Center
                                    ) {
                                        Text("📝 SUFI NOTEPAD", color = if (activeTab == 1) CyberPink else Color.White, fontSize = 10.sp, fontWeight = FontWeight.Bold)
                                    }
                                }

                                if (activeTab == 0) {
                                    // Excel CSV sheet creator
                                    var sheetTopic by remember { mutableStateOf("Shoes Shop Inventory July") }
                                    var isGeneratingSheet by remember { mutableStateOf(false) }
                                    var parsedCsvData by remember { mutableStateOf<List<List<String>>>(emptyList()) }
                                    var csvRawString by remember { mutableStateOf("") }

                                    Text("Sheet Topic or Theme:", color = TextLight, fontSize = 11.sp)
                                    OutlinedTextField(
                                        value = sheetTopic,
                                        onValueChange = { sheetTopic = it },
                                        modifier = Modifier.fillMaxWidth(),
                                        colors = OutlinedTextFieldDefaults.colors(focusedTextColor = Color.White, unfocusedTextColor = Color.White, focusedBorderColor = CyberCyan, unfocusedBorderColor = GridSpace),
                                        singleLine = true
                                    )

                                    Button(
                                        onClick = {
                                            isGeneratingSheet = true
                                            coroutineScope.launch {
                                                val prompt = "Generate a realistic CSV spreadsheet dataset (raw text format, separated ONLY by commas and newlines) for the theme '$sheetTopic'. Output only valid CSV rows, with a header row, and at least 5 data rows. No conversational text."
                                                val res = viewModel.getLLMResponseForModel(viewModel.selectedModel.value, prompt).trim()
                                                csvRawString = res
                                                val lines = res.split("\n").map { it.split(",").map { cell -> cell.trim().replace("\"", "") } }.filter { it.isNotEmpty() && it[0].isNotBlank() }
                                                parsedCsvData = lines
                                                isGeneratingSheet = false
                                            }
                                        },
                                        colors = ButtonDefaults.buttonColors(containerColor = Color(0xFF107C41)),
                                        modifier = Modifier.fillMaxWidth(),
                                        shape = RoundedCornerShape(10.dp),
                                        enabled = !isGeneratingSheet
                                    ) {
                                        if (isGeneratingSheet) {
                                            CircularProgressIndicator(color = Color.White, modifier = Modifier.size(16.dp), strokeWidth = 2.dp)
                                        } else {
                                            Text("AUTO-COMPILE SPREADSHEET 📊", color = Color.White, fontWeight = FontWeight.Bold, fontSize = 11.sp)
                                        }
                                    }

                                    if (parsedCsvData.isNotEmpty()) {
                                        Column(
                                            modifier = Modifier.weight(1f),
                                            verticalArrangement = Arrangement.spacedBy(8.dp)
                                        ) {
